<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to Tradeboard</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .header {
            background-color: #4a90e2;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .content {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 0.8em;
            color: #666;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Welcome to Tradeboard</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <p>Hello {{partnerName}},</p>
        <p>You have been added as an accountability partner for {{userName}} in their trading journey with Tradeboard.
        </p>
        <p>As an accountability partner, you will receive {{frequency}} updates on {{userName}}'s trading performance.
            These updates will help you support and encourage {{userName}} in their trading goals.</p>
        <p>Your role as an accountability partner is crucial in helping traders stay motivated and disciplined. We
            appreciate your commitment to supporting {{userName}}.</p>
        <p>If you have any questions about your role or the updates you'll receive, please don't hesitate to reach out
            to us.</p>
        <p>Thank you for being a part of the Tradeboard community!</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        <p>&copy; 2023 Tradeboard. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
</body>

</html>